<concept id="id_1" class="- topic/topic concept/concept "><title class="- topic/title ">Configure Notifications</title><conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody "><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Sign in to <xref format="html" href="https://testops.katalon.io/login" scope="external" class="- topic/xref ">Katalon TestOps</xref>.</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Click on the <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Avatar</i> icon at the top right corner and choose <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Notification Settings</b>.</p><p class="- topic/p "><image href="Image/TO-Notification_settings_highlighted.png" class="- topic/image "><alt class="- topic/alt ">TestOps Notification Settings</alt></image></p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Select <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Notifications</b> on the left bar.</p><p class="- topic/p ">The <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Notifications</b> page appears as below.</p><p class="- topic/p "><image href="Image/TO-Notification_page_highlighted.png" class="- topic/image "><alt class="- topic/alt ">TestOps Notification setup page</alt></image></p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Choose your options, then click <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Save</b>.</p></li></ol></conbody></concept>